<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
	<meta charset="euc-kr">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>NICE지키미</title>

	<script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/jquery-1.11.3.js"></script>
	<script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/ui.common.js"></script>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../css/zkm/rzm/common.css">
	<script type="text/javascript">
		mbHeader = { title: '케어십알림', prev: true, menu: true };

		$(function () {
			modal.openModal('#modalid1');
		});

		$(document).ready(function () {
			$('#agreeAllChk').uiCheckAll();
		});
	</script>
</head>

<body>
	<div id="wrap">
		<div id="skipNavi"> 
			<a href="#content">본문내용 바로가기</a> 
		</div>
		<!-- header -->
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/header.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/breadcrumbs.js"></script>
		<!--// header -->

		<!-- container -->
		<div id="container">
			<div id="content">
				<div class="section">
					<a href="#modalid1" class="btn base modalOpen">[팝업] 기존 알림 재설정</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--// container -->

		<!-- popup -->
		<div class="uiModal bottom" id="modalid1">
			<div class="modalWrap">
				<button type="button" class="ui-btn typeModalClose"><span class="hidden">닫기</span></button>
				<div class="modalHeader">
					<h1><span>나신용</span>님, 기존 알림을 다시 설정해 주세요.</h1>
				</div>
				<div class="modalContent">
					<!-- content -->
					<div class="inner">
						<ul class="listDot">
							<li>수신하실 알림 종류와 채널을 재설정해 주세요.</li>
							<li>수신채널을 다시 설정하지 않으면 기존 설정이 유지되는 대신 <strong class="bold">케어십알림 서비스를 이용할 수 없으니 반드시 재설정해 주세요.</strong></li>
						</ul>
					
						<div class="agreement sps" id="agreeAllChk">
							<div class="agreeTitle">
								<div class="uiItem">
									<input type="checkbox" id="chk-all" data-chk-item="all"><label for="chk-all"><span>전체 알림 받기</span></label>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="agreeSection">
								<div class="uiAcco">
									<div data-chk-item="list">
										<div class="uiAccoHeader">
											<div class="uiItem"><input type="checkbox" id="chk-item1" data-chk-item="list-item"><label for="chk-item1">모든 알림 받기</label></div>
											<a href="#none" class="uiBtn"><span class="hidden">펼치기</span></a>
										</div>
										<div class="uiAccoContent">
											<div class="subSelBox">
												<ul class="agreeItem">
													<li>
														<input type="checkbox" id="chk-item1-1" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="chk-item1-1">신용변동 알림</label>
													</li>
													<li>
														<input type="checkbox" id="chk-item1-2" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="chk-item1-2">신용조회 알림</label>
													</li>
													<li>
														<input type="checkbox" id="chk-item1-3" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="chk-item1-3">마이데이터 알림</label>
													</li>
												</ul>
											</div>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div data-chk-item="list">
										<div class="uiAccoHeader">
											<div class="uiItem"><input type="checkbox" id="chk-item2" data-chk-item="list-item"><label for="chk-item2">모든 채널 받기</label></div>
											<a href="#none" class="uiBtn"><span class="hidden">펼치기</span></a>
										</div>
										<div class="uiAccoContent">
											<div class="subSelBox">
												<ul class="agreeItem">
													<li>
														<input type="checkbox" id="chk-item2-1" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="chk-item2-1">문자/알림톡</label>
													</li>
													<li>
														<input type="checkbox" id="chk-item2-2" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="chk-item2-2">이메일</label>
													</li>
													<li>
														<input type="checkbox" id="chk-item2-3" data-chk-item="list-sub"><label for="chk-item2-3">앱푸시</label>
													</li>
												</ul>
											</div>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!--// content -->
					<div class="modalBottom">
						<div class="btns">
							<button type="button" class="btn primary"><span>설정내용 저장하기</span></button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- popup -->

		<!-- footer -->
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/footer.js"></script>
		<!--// footer -->
	</div>
</body>

</html>